OL,3,CSuspected hit and run near school
OL,4,Cleaves girl, 13, seriously injured
OL,6,FA teenage girl has been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital with serious injuries
OL,8,Ffollowing a suspected hit and run near
OL,9,Fa school in Whiteley in Hampshire.
OL,11,FThe girl was crossing Glassfield Road
OL,12,Fat 7:47am on Wednesday (14 January)
OL,13,Fwhen she was involved in a collision
OL,14,Fwith a white Volkswagen Crafter van.
OL,16,FThe van didn't stop at the scene, and
OL,17,Fthe girl was taken to hospital with
OL,18,Fserious injuries where she remains.
